reviewText: Great for recapping with the team before tournaments. So much detail in these and usually cheaper than at ATA events.

I did not pay enough attention; thought I was ordering a book, but got a DVD - will see how it works when I get back to it.  I was actually a 2nd Degree Black Belt in the ATA, but had some illness and have not practiced in a long, long time, so hopefully these will work for me.
